{"tid":1545753,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"為什麼兔子會咬電線、籠子? 因為....","createTime":"2019-09-06T04:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T04:42:41.000Z","uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"69a1595c22e0f6c309c560d0d175431a83384d88","tid":1545753,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:38:29.000Z","msg":"咬籠其實是想引主人注意，覺得悶，想出來玩和探索。咬東西是自然的，牠們在大自然是用腳爪和牙齒來掘洞穴。由於牙齒不斷生長，咬東西可幫助磨短。喜歡咬東西的兔子是聰明、親切、喜歡引人注意(或其他兔注意)。有時候主人正在整理東西，牠們過來其實想一起參與。除了提供無限Hay幫助牠們磨牙外，主人可以買草墊、草屋給牠們咬。放牠們出來玩前，記住bunny proof: <span style=\"color: gold;\">用膠管包著電線</span>, 我在宜家傢俬買，五金舖/日本城都應該有得買: <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wWzQScW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwWzQScW.jpg&h=b1868df0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k4i2Jm1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk4i2Jm1.jpg&h=f9b58198&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中文名: 整線器<br />\n<br />\n兔子喜歡引人注意，有時我們看電視時，牠們會躺在電視機前面，幸好牠們不知道我們其實不在留意牠們。因此，經常陪牠們玩是重要，兔子是群體性動物，如果主人沒有空，最好領養多一隻陪伴牠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a6473cffd7626cc802f0ad52e9b7bf474a56a96","tid":1545753,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:39:34.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db8e4a8ab80ac98ee026e3c61024c44842e32f24","tid":1545753,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T04:42:41.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/15